page.title: 15Plants in Sigglesthorne
page.content: In Sigglesthorne plants are found in three main places; private gardens, hedgerows and fields, and patches of woodland. In the{gardens}we found there were some very common plants like the Lupin, Pansy, rose, daffodils and tulips. In{Hedgerows}Cow Parsley, Poppies, Haythorn, Blackthorn, Sweet Cicily, Hogweed and Meadow Cransbill are found. The final area to find Plants is at the edge of fields and small areas of uncultivated patches of{woodland. On our{school field}we found yellow lesser trefoil, ribwort, daisy, dandelion, speedwell, cow parsley, wild parsnip, nettles, rye grass, soft grass, fescue,red campion and goose grass.
